    <section ids="install-from-package-rdo-for-rhel-centos-7" names="install\ from\ package\ (rdo\ for\ rhel/centos\ 7)">
        <title>Install from package (RDO For RHEL/CentOS 7)</title>
        <paragraph>Packages for RHEL/CentOS 7 are available starting from the Mitaka release.</paragraph>
        <enumerated_list enumtype="arabic" prefix="" suffix=".">
            <list_item>
                <paragraph>Install the RDO repositories for your release:</paragraph>
                <literal_block xml:space="preserve">yum install centos-release-openstack-RELEASE # RELEASE can be mitaka, newton or ocata</literal_block>
            </list_item>
            <list_item>
                <paragraph>Install the packages:</paragraph>
                <literal_block xml:space="preserve">yum install openstack-cloudkitty-api openstack-cloudkitty-processor openstack-cloudkitty-ui</literal_block>
            </list_item>
        </enumerated_list>
    </section>
